chunk_content: E N The decision to allow double counting in the above scenario was made following an agreement between PC1, D GHSD/PEPFAR2, and ICPI3 in February 2023 to account for the following considerations: CI • The importance of attributing OVC_SERV Comprehensive results to the proper implementing partner, who E S ensures that all OVC_SERV beneficiaries have a case plan that monitors their progress toward graduation benchmarks (i.e., NOT PC). • Peace Corps receiving attribution for their results against targets (OVC_SERV Preventive). • It is expected that the double counting of PC towards OVC_SERV Preventive will not significantly impact the total number of OVC_SERV Preventive results and therefore Posts will continue to target and report under OVC_SERV Preventive.
